your house, in your car, at your

00:37:14.880 --> 00:37:17.030
place of work, at the gym right now,

00:37:17.040 --> 00:37:19.430
wherever you may be.

00:37:19.440 --> 00:37:22.069
He'll fill you up to the overflow. He's

00:37:22.079 --> 00:37:25.030
no respecter of persons, but He is

00:37:25.040 --> 00:37:29.829
a gentleman. He will not come uninvited.

00:37:29.839 --> 00:37:32.390
He will knock on your door as a polite

00:37:32.400 --> 00:37:34.150
gentleman:

00:37:34.160 --> 00:37:36.310
'Will you let me in?

00:37:36.320 --> 00:37:39.030
Will you let me in?'And so many people

00:37:39.040 --> 00:37:40.630
think, 'Well, how come God's done

00:37:40.630 --> 00:37:40.640
this?'No,

00:37:40.640 --> 00:37:44.790
He's a gentleman,

00:37:44.800 --> 00:37:46.630
very proper:

00:37:46.640 --> 00:37:48.790
'Will you let me in?'He's at your door

00:37:48.800 --> 00:37:51.829
and He's knocking.

00:37:51.839 --> 00:37:53.349
And so many people say, 'I don't hear

00:37:53.349 --> 00:37:53.359
God.'I

00:37:53.359 --> 00:37:55.829
don't believe that. The Bible

00:37:55.839 --> 00:37:58.310
says His sheep will hear His voice, and a

00:37:58.320 --> 00:38:01.750
stranger's voice they will not follow.

00:38:01.760 --> 00:38:03.910
I believe with all my heart that He will

00:38:03.920 --> 00:38:06.710
speak to you right where you are in your

00:38:06.720 --> 00:38:08.790
house. He'll speak to you. He's that

00:38:08.800 --> 00:38:12.310
still small voice inside of you. He's

00:38:12.320 --> 00:38:15.990
not thundering, 'Hello, I'm here to talk to

00:38:16.000 --> 00:38:19.910
you today!'It's still, small, gentle,

00:38:19.920 --> 00:38:23.510
quiet. And the more you develop it, the

00:38:23.520 --> 00:38:25.589
more you listen and the more you yield:

00:38:25.599 --> 00:38:28.710
'Father, here am I. Fill me.

00:38:28.720 --> 00:38:32.310
I'm thirsty. I'm

00:38:32.310 --> 00:38:32.320
hungry.'Diana

00:38:32.320 --> 00:38:33.990
doesn't have to yell for me to

00:38:34.000 --> 00:38:36.630
know her voice. She can be at the other

00:38:36.640 --> 00:38:38.150
side of the room and just barely speak, and I

00:38:38.160 --> 00:38:40.150
know exactly

00:38:40.160 --> 00:38:42.550
that's her. You know why? Because I've

00:38:42.560 --> 00:38:45.990
practiced being around her. I'm

00:38:46.000 --> 00:38:48.390
familiar with her. And the more you

00:38:48.400 --> 00:38:50.069
become familiar with the Father by

00:38:50.079 --> 00:38:52.950
reading His word on a day-to-day

00:38:52.950 --> 00:38:52.960
basis—reading

00:38:52.960 --> 00:38:55.190
His Bible, reading and

00:38:55.190 --> 00:38:55.200
praying—you

00:38:55.200 --> 00:38:57.750
will become familiar with

00:38:57.760 --> 00:39:01.270
Him, and the louder His voice

00:39:01.280 --> 00:39:04.870
will become within you.

00:39:04.880 --> 00:39:07.430
The reason why a lot of you say, 'I

00:39:07.440 --> 00:39:08.950
don't hear Him,'is because you've not

00:39:08.950 --> 00:39:08.960
spent

00:39:08.960 --> 00:39:12.230
enough time at His feet and you've

00:39:12.240 --> 00:39:14.630
not read enough of His word. And you get

00:39:14.640 --> 00:39:16.230
this word down, and it will change you

00:39:16.240 --> 00:39:19.030
from the inside out.

00:39:19.040 --> 00:39:20.390
So that's why I would try to tell

00:39:20.390 --> 00:39:20.400
you—because

00:39:20.400 --> 00:39:23.270
I felt to say that

00:39:23.270 --> 00:39:23.280
tonight—that

00:39:23.280 --> 00:39:25.349
God's not hiding from you. He

00:39:25.359 --> 00:39:27.510
said, 'Those that seek me will find

00:39:27.510 --> 00:39:27.520
me.

00:39:27.520 --> 00:39:29.910
Those that knock, I'll open the

00:39:29.910 --> 00:39:29.920
door.'So,

00:39:29.920 --> 00:39:32.390
yeah, there is kind of like

00:39:32.390 --> 00:39:32.400
a—how

00:39:32.400 --> 00:39:34.630
hungry, how desperate are you seeking

00:39:34.640 --> 00:39:37.270
Him, and you'll find Him. There is a

00:39:37.280 --> 00:39:39.910
point of

00:39:39.920 --> 00:39:42.470
pursuit.

00:39:42.480 --> 00:39:45.510
You have to pursue Him.

00:39:45.520 --> 00:39:48.470
How bad do you want your life

00:39:48.480 --> 00:39:50.550
changed?

00:39:50.560 --> 00:39:55.109
It's not lazy, and there's no microwave.

00:39:55.119 --> 00:39:57.829
It's a slow cooker. Relationship with

00:39:57.839 --> 00:39:59.990
the Lord seems to be a slow cooker. It's

00:40:00.000 --> 00:40:02.790
not a microwave, but it's

00:40:02.800 --> 00:40:04.550
worth it. When you cook something in a slow

00:40:04.560 --> 00:40:06.069
cooker, it tastes a lot better than it

00:40:06.069 --> 00:40:06.079
does

00:40:06.079 --> 00:40:08.069
in a microwave.

00:40:08.079 --> 00:40:09.589
And the more you cook in that slow

00:40:09.599 --> 00:40:11.589
cooker, you're thinking, 'That tastes

00:40:11.599 --> 00:40:14.390
really good,'versus, 'I microwaved that

00:40:14.400 --> 00:40:18.710
pizza, and that is

00:40:18.710 --> 00:40:18.720
nasty.'There

00:40:18.720 --> 00:40:21.829
is a difference.

00:40:21.839 --> 00:40:25.589
And it is those

00:40:25.589 --> 00:40:25.599
tugs—it's

00:40:25.599 --> 00:40:27.030
like trying to explain it to my little

00:40:27.040 --> 00:40:28.470
girl. She's always, 'Daddy, how do you

00:40:28.480 --> 00:40:31.190
hear God like you do?'It's the

00:40:31.200 --> 00:40:34.150
little tugs. It's

00:40:34.160 --> 00:40:37.270
learning. It's a dance.

00:40:37.280 --> 00:40:40.390
He leads, I follow. It's a dance.

00:40:40.400 --> 00:40:42.310
It's like having a beautiful

00:40:42.320 --> 00:40:43.829
ballroom

00:40:43.839 --> 00:40:45.910
dance that you dance with the Holy

00:40:45.920 --> 00:40:48.390
Spirit, like you would see a beautiful

00:40:48.400 --> 00:40:50.550
couple dancing.

00:40:50.560 --> 00:40:53.990
And you dance, and you let him lead, and

00:40:54.000 --> 00:40:56.550
you follow. But it's very beautiful, and

00:40:56.560 --> 00:41:00.790
it's not forceful.

00:41:00.800 --> 00:41:03.109
It's not like,

00:41:03.119 --> 00:41:06.230
'We got to make this

00:41:06.230 --> 00:41:06.240
happen,'all

00:41:06.240 --> 00:41:09.589
chaos. It's very beautiful. It's a

00:41:09.599 --> 00:41:12.630
symphony. It flows when you jump in the

00:41:12.640 --> 00:41:14.950
river and you go down the lazy river.

00:41:14.960 --> 00:41:18.150
It's a symphony. And the more you become

00:41:18.160 --> 00:41:20.630
close to him, you flow in that river in

00:41:20.640 --> 00:41:22.710
a greater capacity.

00:41:22.720 --> 00:41:25.829
I can hear now when other people pray

00:41:25.839 --> 00:41:29.349
beside me in my personal time. And I

00:41:29.359 --> 00:41:31.190
know certain people in their prayer

00:41:31.200 --> 00:41:32.630
when they're praying beside me. The Lord

00:41:32.640 --> 00:41:34.230
will have you in the spirit realm;

00:41:34.240 --> 00:41:36.309
they're assigned to pray for the same

00:41:36.319 --> 00:41:37.750
thing. And I'll say, 'Oh, that's that

00:41:37.760 --> 00:41:40.150
sister from such-and-such

00:41:40.150 --> 00:41:40.160
place.'I'll

00:41:40.160 --> 00:41:42.150
know that. Usually the Lord will

00:41:42.160 --> 00:41:44.630
reveal to me how old they are, where

00:41:44.640 --> 00:41:46.630
they are, and who they are, and they're

00:41:46.640 --> 00:41:48.390
praying beside me because you can feel

00:41:48.400 --> 00:41:51.349
it. It's a symphony, you know. One might

00:41:51.359 --> 00:41:54.550
be the drums, one might be the

00:41:54.560 --> 00:41:57.349
saxophone, one might be the tuba, one

00:41:57.359 --> 00:41:59.270
might be the baritone, whatever. All

00:41:59.280 --> 00:42:01.190
these different instruments—the clarinet, all these

00:42:01.200 --> 00:42:03.990
beautiful noises—make an orchestra

00:42:04.000 --> 00:42:07.109
before the Father. And I know when the

00:42:07.119 --> 00:42:10.069
flute comes in, whenever the sister that

00:42:10.079 --> 00:42:10.950
plays the flute—you know what I'm

00:42:10.960 --> 00:42:12.150
saying? That's what I'm trying to do; I'm

00:42:12.160 --> 00:42:13.589
trying to make it as easy as I can for

00:42:13.599 --> 00:42:15.589
y'all. But the more you start flowing

00:42:15.599 --> 00:42:17.510
with the Spirit of God, you can

00:42:17.520 --> 00:42:19.109
intertwine. You can pray with

00:42:19.119 --> 00:42:20.710
people in the

00:42:20.720 --> 00:42:23.829
middle of the night, and you get familiar. And I say, 'I know who that

00:42:23.829 --> 00:42:23.839
is praying.

00:42:23.839 --> 00:42:27.030
I

00:42:27.040 --> 00:42:29.750
know who that is

00:42:29.750 --> 00:42:29.760
praying.'I

00:42:29.760 --> 00:42:33.030
may not know her

00:42:33.040 --> 00:42:34.870
personally, but I know that feeling

00:42:34.880 --> 00:42:37.109
because they helped me pray before. And

00:42:37.119 --> 00:42:38.390
it's just getting familiar with the

00:42:38.400 --> 00:42:40.230
Spirit of God. And people, your brothers

00:42:40.240 --> 00:42:42.069
and sisters in Christ, you'll feel them

00:42:42.079 --> 00:42:44.710
praying with you. I know that may sound

00:42:44.720 --> 00:42:46.390
really way out there, but it's just

00:42:46.400 --> 00:42:51.510
developed. It just takes time.

00:42:51.520 --> 00:42:53.430
Praying with people at the church, you

00:42:53.440 --> 00:42:56.069
add your supply. That's what I'm trying

00:42:56.079 --> 00:42:58.550
to tell you. You add your supply. You

00:42:58.560 --> 00:42:59.990
know, when they're not there at church

00:43:00.000 --> 00:43:01.670
and they're not praying with you,

00:43:01.680 --> 00:43:03.670
they add their supply when

00:43:03.680 --> 00:43:05.990
they come, and you come together.

00:43:08.319 --> 00:43:13.349
Many hands make light work,

00:43:13.359 --> 00:43:14.870
and when they're not there, you

00:43:14.880 --> 00:43:16.550
feel their absence. That's why I said

00:43:16.560 --> 00:43:18.550
it's all hands on deck, even with this

00:43:18.560 --> 00:43:20.069
channel,

00:43:20.079 --> 00:43:21.910
us coming together and praying together

00:43:21.920 --> 00:43:24.230
more and more, praying as a

00:43:24.240 --> 00:43:27.190
family. Because you live in Australia, and

00:43:27.200 --> 00:43:29.990
you live in New Zealand, and you

00:43:29.990 --> 00:43:30.000
live—I

00:43:30.000 --> 00:43:31.670
