00:43:34.319 --> 00:43:36.390
South America, in Brazil,'and all these

00:43:36.400 --> 00:43:37.910
other places, and I go, 'Wow, that's

00:43:37.920 --> 00:43:40.150
amazing, we pray with you the whole time.'And

00:43:40.150 --> 00:43:40.160
some

00:43:40.160 --> 00:43:41.910
say, 'Well, we live in South

00:43:41.910 --> 00:43:41.920
Africa.'People

00:43:41.920 --> 00:43:43.270
say, 'I pray with you

00:43:43.280 --> 00:43:45.109
in South Africa every day,'and I go, 'Wow,

00:43:45.119 --> 00:43:48.630
that's amazing, in South Africa. Wow,

00:43:48.640 --> 00:43:50.790
what a

00:43:50.790 --> 00:43:50.800
blessing.'But

00:43:50.800 --> 00:43:53.349
every one of us brings our supply to

00:43:53.359 --> 00:43:55.030
the need of what we're praying for

00:43:55.040 --> 00:43:56.790
that day,

00:43:56.800 --> 00:43:59.589
