00:49:04.240 --> 00:49:06.150
woe,

00:49:06.150 --> 00:49:06.160
woe,

00:49:06.160 --> 00:49:09.109
America,

00:49:09.119 --> 00:49:12.950
for a great shaking is coming.

00:49:12.950 --> 00:49:12.960
Woe,

00:49:12.960 --> 00:49:14.950
America.'And

00:49:14.960 --> 00:49:18.390
