00:49:57.920 --> 00:50:01.190
The storm is no longer coming. It is

00:50:01.190 --> 00:50:01.200
here.'I

00:50:01.200 --> 00:50:04.630
heard them

00:50:04.630 --> 00:50:04.640
say—five

00:50:04.640 --> 00:50:07.750
angels,

00:50:07.760 --> 00:50:09.750
five—and

00:50:09.760 --> 00:50:13.109
they said, 'Woe,

00:50:13.109 --> 00:50:13.119
